short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A quicker way to search the web and add productivity to your day

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Qwik Biz Tools is a one-stop extension for all of your desktop productivity and browsing needs.
Built for convenience, by simply opening a new tab you will get immediate access to an extensive list of business tools to select from, and enjoy a quick & seamless online search experience straight from your browser.

Installing this extension will replace your browsers new tab. Allowing you to quickly find and view search results directly from your new tab. By clicking "Add to Chrome", you accept and agree to installing the Qwik Biz Tools Chrome extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab to that provided by the service with results by Microsoft Bing, and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

Not only will you have immediate access to the most popular business productivity tools available online today available all on the one same page. But along with the practical functionality and elegant design, this extension also displays an easy view of time & date, as well as providing quick links to some popular social media sites.

With so much capability and features right at your fingertips, you’ll be glad you installed this extension. With the added comfort of knowing that you can uninstall at any time should you wish.
